---
layout: default
title: Check out Gui Ferreira talks
description: "Talks about Software Development by Gui Ferreira| guiferreira.me"
---

<section class="my-auto">
  <div class="mx-auto flow">
    <h1>Check out my talks</h1>
    <h2 class="mt-6 font-sans text-2xl font-light mb-20">
      Here you can find some of my talks.
      <br/> Want me to speak at your event?
      <a href="/about">Get in touch!</a>
    </h2>
    <ul>
      {%- for talk in talks.all -%}
        <li class="mt-20">
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold">{{ talk.title }}
          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2">
            {% if talk.description %}
              {% multilineDescription talk.description %}
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <h5 class="mt-5 font-semibold">Presentations</h5>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <ul>
              {%- for presentation in talk.presentations.reverse() -%}
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <a class="text-primary hover:text-secondary " alt="{{ presentation.name }} | {{ presentation.date }}" href="{{ presentation.url }}">{{ presentation.name }}</a>
                  {% if presentation.recording %}
                    <a class="text-primary hover:text-secondary flex-1 ml-2" href="{{ presentation.recording }}">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" class="h-7 w-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M19.615 3.184c-3.604-.246-11.631-.245-15.23 0-3.897.266-4.356 2.62-4.385 8.816.029 6.185.484 8.549 4.385 8.816 3.6.245
                        11.626.246 15.23 0 3.897-.266 4.356-2.62 4.385-8.816-.029-6.185-.484-8.549-4.385-8.816zm-10.615 12.816v-8l8 3.993-8
                        4.007z"/>
                      </svg>
                    </a>
                  {% endif %}
                </li>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>